'''赫里福德'''（'''Hereford'''）是位於[[英國|英國]][[赫里福德郡|赫里福德郡]]的[[英國城市地位|城市]]、[[民政教区|民政教区]]。人口約五万<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.herefordshire.gov.uk/factsandfigures/docs/Research/Current_Hfds_Population_Digest.pdf |title=Herefordshire Council Facts and Figures |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2011-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609044054/http://www.herefordshire.gov.uk/factsandfigures/docs/research/current_hfds_population_digest.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是赫里福德郡郡治和郡內最大的城市。赫里福德在1189年獲得了[[英國城市地位|城市地位]]<ref name="charters">{{cite web | url= http://www.herefordwebpages.co.uk/charters.shtml | title= The Royal Charters of the City of Hereford | work= Hereford Web Pages | accessdate= 2011-09-07 | archive-date= 2012-01-15 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120115175947/http://www.herefordwebpages.co.uk/charters.shtml | dead-url= no }}</ref>，在2000年10月，赫里福德的城市地位得到了再次確認<ref>Beckett, J V (2005). ''City status in the British Isles, 1830–2002'', Historical urban studies. Aldershot: Ashgate.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.herefordcitycouncil.gov.uk/history/municipal-history/charters/ |title=Hereford City Council Charter |publisher=Herefordcitycouncil.gov.uk |date= |accessdate=2012-01-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212221809/http://www.herefordcitycouncil.gov.uk/history/municipal-history/charters/ |archivedate=2012-02-12 }}</ref>。赫里福德是一個重要的農貿中心。[[赫里福德座堂|赫里福德的大教堂]]建于1204年，迄今仍在使用<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ads.ahds.ac.uk/catalogue/adsdata/arch-769-1/ahds/dissemination/pdf/vol04/4_069_080.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-03-06 |archive-date=2010-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101217231722/http://ads.ahds.ac.uk/catalogue/adsdata/arch-769-1/ahds/dissemination/pdf/vol04/4_069_080.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.localhistories.org/hereford.html |title=A History of Hereford |publisher=Localhistories.org |date= |accessdate=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2012-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107033042/http://www.localhistories.org/hereford.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。赫里福德還每年舉辦合唱節。市內有眾多公共休閒設施。

